      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. This example benefits from a reinforced rear subframe and a recently serviced VANOS system, ensuring valve timing precision and solenoid reliability. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings and a factory limited-slip differential that provides exceptional corner-exit traction. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its mileage, the hydraulic steering remains communicative and the high-revving powerplant pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline",
